apps.localizedDescription:
from @binnichtaktivsipas |
--------------------------
YouTube OLED

YouTube Plus: A tweak that enhances the YouTube experience by removing ads, enabling background playback and offering over 60 customization options. 

DontEatMyContent Prevent the notch/Dynamic Island from munching on 2:1 video content in YouTube 

YouPiP Enable native PiP in iOS YouTube app

Gonerino YouTube tweak to remove videos uploaded by specific channels 

Return YouTube Dislike Bring back dislikes on iOS YouTube

Open in YouTube shortcut Copy a YouTube video link and run this shortcut to open in YouTube OLED without ads

Open in Youtube extension enables "Open In" for sideloaded Youtube in Safari without any need to download other Opener apps / Shortcuts. (Shorts are now supported too)

Huge thanks to @dvntms for this great tweak. If you want to use the latest YouTube Plus betas subscribe to his Patreon

minimum OS version 15.0

AppStore link | Donate | Get your own signing cert

apps.localizedDescription:

YouTube OLED

YouTube Plus: A tweak that enhances the YouTube experience by removing ads, enabling background playback and offering over 60 customization options.
